OL,4,CChina cuts children's online gaming to
OL,5,Cone hour
OL,6, Online gamers under the age of 18 will
OL,7, only be allowed to play for an hour on
OL,8, Fridays, weekends and holidays, China's
OL,9, video game regulator has said.
OL,11,FThe National Press and Publication
OL,12,FAdministration told state-run news
OL,13,Fagency Xinhua that game-playing would
OL,14,Fbe only allowed between 8pm to 9pm.
OL,16,FIt also instructed gaming companies to
OL,17,Fprevent children playing outside these
OL,18,Ftimes.
OL,20,FEarlier this month a state media outlet
OL,21,Fbranded online games "spiritual opium".
